name: Tufts Medical Center
description:
Tufts Medical Center is an internationally-respected academic medical center – a teaching hospital where they pride themselves not only in the sophistication of the care they provide but the compassionate way in which they provide it. They care for all patients from the tiniest newborns at their full-service pediatric hospital, Floating Hospital for Children to centenarians in their specialized Geriatrics clinic.

https://www.tuftsmedicalcenter.org
